Check Operation of Applications:

sudo systemctl status bitcoind.service
sudo systemctl status fulcrum.service
sudo systemctl status lnd.service
sudo systemctl status RTL.service
sudo systemctl status boltzd.service
sudo systemctl status loopd.service
sudo systemctl status litd.service

sudo systemctl restart bitcoind.service
sudo systemctl restart fulcrum.service
sudo systemctl restart lnd.service
sudo systemctl restart RTL.service
sudo systemctl restart boltzd.service
sudo systemctl restart loopd.service
sudo systemctl restart litd.service

sudo systemctl stop bitcoind.service
sudo systemctl start bitcoind.service

Blockchain and Block Commands:

bitcoin-cli getblockchaininfo - Get information about the current state of the blockchain.
bitcoin-cli getblockcount - Get the current block height.
bitcoin-cli gettxoutsetinfo - Get statistics about the UTXO (Unspent Transaction Output) set.
bitcoin-cli getconnectioncount - Get the number of connections to other nodes in the Bitcoin network.
bitcoin-cli start - Start bitcoin-core
bitcoin-cli stop - Stop bitcoin-core
bitcoind - Start bitcoin in the background

To Restart Samourai Wallet Dojo:

cd /home/humble/dojo-app/samourai/docker/my-dojo/ -> type: sudo docker-compose up

To Restart Mempool:

cd ~/mempool/docker/ -> type: sudo docker-compose up 

PORTS:
Mempool->IPaddress:4080
Ride The Lightning(RTL)->IPaddress:3000
